def test_msgctxt(self):
        translations = DummyTranslations('result')
        result = self._callFUT(
            translations, u('p\xf8f'), 'plural', 1, context='button')
        self.assertEqual(translations.params,
                         (u('button\x04p\xf8f'), 'plural', 1))
